{"story":{"group_1":[{"bg":"bg_adv_21211.jpg","bgm":"bgm03_story07","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":0,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"フェリシア","textRight":"なに？@オレ、何かやべーこと言った？","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"やちよ","textLeft":"言ったわよ…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"いろは","textLeft":"鶴乃ちゃん…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100101}],"textLeft":"このお店のこと、@すごく大切に思ってるんだよ？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":301}],"textLeft":"それをあんな風に笑われたら…@そりゃ怒るよ…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100501}],"textRight":"ふーん"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_011.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":100,"mouthOpen":1}],"textRight":"でも、いつもは、キレたら@ガキみてーにわーわー喚くのにな"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":0}],"textRight":"急に腹でも壊したのかと思ったぜ"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"やちよ","textLeft":"――っ!!@フェリ…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"いろは","textLeft":"何でそんな風に言ってられるの？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100101}],"textLeft":"鶴乃ちゃん、それくらい@ショックだったってことだよ？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100201,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"やちよ","textLeft":"（環さん…）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501}],"textRight":"ぁあん？@オレがわりーってのか？"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":401,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"いろは","textLeft":"悪いよ@人が傷付くようなこと言って…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501}],"textRight":"別に鶴乃のこと傷付けようとか@思ってねーし"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":100}],"textRight":"オレはただ、しょーじきに@思ったこと言っただけじゃんかよ"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":0}],"textLeft":"思ってたら、@何でも言っていいの!?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"やちよ","textLeft":"環さん…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":300}],"textRight":"何だよ、それ…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":0}],"textRight":"…じゃぁっ…@嘘つけば良かったのかよ！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501}],"textRight":"思ってもねーこと@言えば良かった、ってのかよ！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":401,"pos":0}],"nameLeft":"いろは","textLeft":"嘘つけば、いいだなんて@思ってない…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"嘘をつくことと…@相手を思いやることは…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100101}],"textLeft":"全然同じなんかじゃないよ…!?"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":301}],"textLeft":"相手の気持ちも考えずに@何でも言うのは…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"誠実さなんかじゃない…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_021.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1}],"textLeft":"…っはぁ…はぁ…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_020.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":0}],"textRight":"――っ!!@オレはっ…！"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100501,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"（…何で？@何でだよ…）","turnEffect":"thinking"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textRight":"（オレのせいで…@鶴乃は傷付いたってのかよ…）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0}],"textRight":"（…悪口言ってやろうとか…@そんなんじゃなかったのに…）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100501,"lipSynch":0}],"textRight":"（…なんでそんな…）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textRight":"（オレのこと…ひでぇ奴みてぇに@言うんだよ…！）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":2,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":200,"mouthOpen":1}],"textRight":"――っ!!@もう、分ッかんねーよっ!!","turnEffect":"stop"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":400,"mouthOpen":1,"pos":0},{"effect":"fadeout","id":100501}],"nameLeft":"やちよ","textLeft":"…ちょっと…！@フェリシアっ…!!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":401,"pos":2}],"nameRight":"いろは","textRight":"――っ!!"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":0}],"textRight":"ごめんなさい…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"id":100101,"motion":200}],"textRight":"フェリシアちゃんまで…@出ていっちゃった…"},{"chara":[{"cheek":-1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":200}],"textLeft":"謝るところじゃないでしょ@賛同したから、黙って聞いてたの"},{"chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_014.exp.json","id":100201,"motion":301}],"textLeft":"良いこと言うじゃない"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100101,"motion":0,"mouthOpen":1}],"textRight":"やちよさん…"},{"bg":"bg_adv_13042.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":0,"pos":1}],"nameCenter":"フェリシア","textCenter":"（心の中では思ってても、@隠せってことかよ…!?）","turnChangeIn":"fadeIn","turnChangeOut":"fadeOut"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100501,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"（…オレは、ただ…@正直にいようって…）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100501,"lipSynch":0}],"textCenter":"（…一緒にいたいから…@正直でいたい、って…）"},{"chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_030.exp.json","id":100501,"lipSynch":0,"motion":300}],"textCenter":"（…そう…思ってたのに…@…一緒に…いたいって…）"},{"nameNarration":"フェリシア","narration":"“相手を思う”って何だ？","narrationBg":"bg_adv_11042.jpg","narrationEffect":"in"},{"narration":"…鶴乃を思えば…@どうするのが正解だったんだよ…"},{"narration":"…オレのせいで…@鶴乃は傷付いた…"},{"narration":"…鶴乃を思うって…@鶴乃…"},{"bg":"bg_adv_21143.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":0,"face":"mtn_ex_050.exp.json","id":100501,"motion":0}],"nameCenter":"フェリシア","narrationEffect":"out","textCenter":"――っ!!@…ここ"},{"bg":"bg_adv_11021.jpg","chara":[{"cheek":1,"face":"mtn_ex_010.exp.json","id":100301